<div>22. The largest value of \(3\sin^2\theta+2\cos^2\theta-1\) is<br/>
A. \(1\).<br/>
B. \(\dfrac{3}{2}\).<br/>
C. \(2\).<br/>
D. \(3\).<br/>
E. \(4\).
